data.description: Welcome to your new home in the Lakeland Estates subdivision of Raleigh, located conveniently to shopping and major highways, ensuring easy access to all that Raleigh has to offer!  Situated on over a quarter of an acre, this spacious 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence offers the perfect combination of comfort and convenience.  All four bedrooms are conveniently located upstairs offering privacy and separation from the living areas.  Other features include:  2 car garage, BRAND NEW dishwasher, fridge, and wifi enabled range,  NEW ROOF Oct 2023, water heater 2019, and ceramic tile foyer.  Don't miss your chance to call this wonderful property, home. Schedule a showing today and discover the endless possibilities awaiting you in Lakeland Estates!
